
Host: website.local

-------------------------
Installation:
-------------------------
1. Install Drupal using composer command.
2. Create database named cloudblue.
3. Host Creation in local system (Optional)

-------------------------
Theme Setup:
-------------------------
Setting up theme directory structure (ie: web/themes/custom/cloudblue) and pasting everything from the html template.
Converting html template into drupal theme by (integrating liabraries, files and images).

-------------------------
