Sections developed by using Views:
----------------------------------
1. Slider
2. Services
3. Tab Options
4. Testimonial
5. Worldwide Sheets
6. Events
7. Industrial Solutions Tabs
8. News

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Sections developed with the help of Paragraphs and Custom block type:
---------------------------------------------------------------------
1. About Us
2. Counter
3. Industrial Solutions
4. Catalog Banner
5. Call-to-action

*Topbar, Footer logo, Social Icons, Copyright and Cookies fields are developed by using Theme Preprocess functions.

-------------------------
Mudules Used:
-------------------------
1. Pathauto (for set created content path or URL automatically)
2. Context (for separate page contents what we want to show and which page or content type)
3. Admin-toolbar (for admin toolbar dropdown on hover)
4. Module-filter (for filtering modules easily)
5. Paragraphs (for creating dynamic sections)
6. Coffee (for shortcut navigation in admin panel)
7. Svg-image (for upload svg type image)
8. Date-range-formatter (for events date)
9. Devel (for Shortcuts and generating dummy data)
10. Linked-field (for edit machine name)
11. Simple-login (for admin login panel)
12. Webform (for Popup form)







